column2: select   l.oiii_#_flux,l.oiii_#_flux_err,l.nii_#_flux,l.nii_#_flux_err,l.h_alpha_flux,l.h_alpha_flux_err,l.h_beta_flux,l.h_beta_flux_err into for_BPT    from galSpecline as l join SpecObjALL as s    on l.specObjID=s.specObjID join galSpecinfo as i   on l.specObjID=i.specObjID          where   s.sciencePrimary=#
